title: Georgia Senate 2026 - Day 10 AM Session
summary:
Here is a structured markdown summary of the Georgia Senate 2026 - Day 10 AM Session:

This session focused on the introduction of several new bills and resolutions in the Georgia Senate. There were no major pieces of substantive legislation passed, but the session included routine procedures, recognitions of guests, and a morning devotion.

- **SB 439**: To amend the Official Code of Georgia related to public health services
